 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/289469/', '', 'Latanoprost, Methazolamide, Neostigmine, Pilocarpine, Betaxolol, Diclofenamide, Bimatoprost, Travoprost, Carteolol, Brinzolamide, Acetazolamide, More', '', 1767369485);
